.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-MPP-STATUS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-mpp-status \- show multi-part payment status and part count
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-mpp-status
.I payment_hash
.SH DESCRIPTION
Looks up a payment by
.I payment_hash
and returns its status plus the number of payment parts (MPP).
Returns
.B {"error":"not_found"}
if the hash is unknown.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{payment_hash, status, parts, amount_msat, amount_sent_msat}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-status (1),
.BR lightning-payment-list (1)
